  "title": "Variant Bookshelves",
  "description": "Bookshelves in all wood types",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Bookshelves/BH_VB_Title.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Bookshelves adds a new Bookshelf for each available Plank type added to your game </span><br /><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\"> (where support has been provided)</span><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7688001/184733794-6cf42e59-b61d-438f-821e-76b672ad648f.png\" /></p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></span></strong></span></h6>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">This is not just a simple recolour of bookshelves,<br />care and attention has been taken to ensure optimal experience when using this mod.</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">All textures have been compressed (without any negative impact) to keep the mod file size to an absolute minimum.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">All textures are manually created using the hex colours from the appropriate planks to ensure they look correct.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Fabric load conditions have been used to ensure your console is not full of errors when compatible mods are not installed.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Un-crafting for all variants back to vanilla has been included in case of any issues.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Vanilla bookshelf renamed to Oak and recoloured slightly to better fit the Oak wood type.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">All added bookshelves work with the vanilla Enchanting Table</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>Please also consider downloading my other mods</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Barrels -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-barrels-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-barrels-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Composters -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-composters-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-composters-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Crafting Tables -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-crafting-tables-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-crafting-tables-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Grindstones -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-grindstones-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-grindstones-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Lanterns -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-lanterns-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-lanterns-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Shields -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-tiered-shields-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-tiered-shields-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Sticks &amp; Stuff -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-sticks-stuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-sticks-stuff</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Variant Weapons &amp; Tools -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-weapons-tools-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-weapons-tools-fabric</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/tmwxB2sceU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/shingekinokyojin/images/4/42/Discord_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"64\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Bookshelves/BH_VB_BisectPromo.png\" /></p>",
